description: This duplex penthouse unit is located in the heart of Southie, steps from Thomas Park/Dorchester Heights. The unit has two distinct levels of living, with the living room and kitchen on the first floor, and the bedrooms on the second floor. The third floor headhouse (featuring a bar & refrigerator) and walk-out roof deck (completely redone in 2022) provide city views from the Back Bay to the Seaport. Additional highlights include - central AC, crown molding, 10ft ceilings, Brazilian cherry floors, granite countertops, surround sound, 3 levels of outdoor decks, and 2 gas fireplaces. The building is entirely owner-occupied and the association has ample reserves.
